snippet: Colombia international James Rodriguez said he had received offers to leave European champions Real Madrid and was considering his future in order to play more often....
lead_paragraph: Colombia international James Rodriguez said he had received offers to leave European champions Real Madrid and was considering his future in order to play more often.

headline.main: Out of Favour Rodriguez Cannot Guarantee He Will Stay at Real
